The paper presents a nonlinear differentiator that improves dynamical performance and robustness, while reducing chattering and noise. This suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of control systems (cs.SY), machine learning (cs.LG), robotics (cs.RO), neural networks (cs.NE), or artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
